# An h1 header

Paragraphs are separated by a blank line.

2nd paragraph. _Italic_, **bold**, and `monospace`. Itemized lists
look like:

- this one
- that one
- the other one

> Block quotes are
> written like so.
>
> They can span multiple paragraphs,
> if you like.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="preview col">
      <div class="header">
        PREVIEW
      </div>
      <h1>An h1 header</h1>
      <p>Paragraphs are separated by a blank line.</p>
      <p>Second paragraph. <i>Italic</i>, <b>bold</b>, and
        <span style="font-family: monospace;">monospace</span>.
        Itemized lists look like:

        <ul>
          <li>this one</li>
          <li>that one</li>
          <li>the other one</li>
        </ul>

        <blockquote>
          <p>Block quotes are written like so.</p>
          <p>They can span multiple paragraphs, if you like.
        </blockquote>
